<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī vijayābdū[*da]ya śālivāhana śalavo 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ruṣaṁbulu 1449 Agunēṭi vi 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>krutisaṁvatcara jēṣṭa śuda 5 ni ma 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁgaḷavāra<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>nu śrīma(ṁnu)Nmahārā 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>(ṁ)jādhirāja rājaparamēśvara śrī vīrapra 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tāpa śrīvīranarasi<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>hva Acyutarāyyadēva 
<lb n="7"/>mahārāyalu pritivi rājyaṁcēyucu 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁḍagānu Ayaparasaya vārkipuṇya 
</p>

<p>The rest of the record is lost.</p>

